{"tid":1857600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃埔花園11期1座武漢肺炎男患者母親初步檢測為陽性","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T02:25:58.000Z","uid":28114,"like":96,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"11b0dda72f390702a6c8d18c772f0993b1d8fd22","tid":1857600,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"【#社區消息 | 黃埔花園11期1座武漢肺炎男患者母親初步檢測為陽性】<br />\n前晚確診武漢肺炎的黃埔花園11期1座居民的母親昨日起發燒由隔離營送院，初步檢測為陽性，現時在伊院等候覆檢結果。<br />\n------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxKiUDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxKiUDQ.jpg&h=8843b4de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Whampaper/photos/a.885842434857052/2653049348136343/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWhampaper%2Fphotos%2Fa.885842434857052%2F2653049348136343%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9D%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=ca46ba76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Whampaper/photos/a.885842434857052/2653049348136343/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"7e4af3c83a5cd2135098dfba6f573d497c2abb44","tid":1857600,"uid":28114,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"黃埔又多一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6900a3402e91a49c75196b93ced4cfcfa2f86a3","tid":1857600,"uid":295548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"《天滅中共賦》<br />\n<br />\n共黨臣民 作惡多端<br />\n外侵諸邦 內屠義士<br />\n黃禍所至 寸草不生<br />\n禍國殃民 血債累累<br />\n習妖維尼 逆天而行<br />\n自立為帝 天怒人怨<br />\n庚子伊始 天譴將臨<br />\n大仙報夢 國運已盡<br />\n共黨治下 必有七患<br />\n正月武肺 播毒中原<br />\n二月流感 飛禽盡亡<br />\n三月地震 血流成河<br />\n四月豬瘟 百物騰升<br />\n五月飢荒 易子而食<br />\n六月內戰 析骸而爨<br />\n七月水災 長江決堤<br />\n炎共將亡 水德當立<br />\n歲在庚子 天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCW3BCS.jpg\" data-t